课程（English for Professional Purposes: Communications Practice）</li>	<li>法律英语课程（English for Professional Purposes: Law）</li>	<li>国际与公共事务英语课程（English for Professional Purposes: SIPA）</li>	<li>社会工作（夏季）英语课程（English for Professional Purposes: Social Work (Summer)）</li>	<li>社会工作（秋季）英语课程（English for Social Work (Fall)）</li>	<li>国际教师培训课程（International Teaching Fellows Training）*(1)</li></ul><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>哥伦比亚大学语言课程并非为因语言成绩未达到学位项要求而被授予的条件录取（Conditional offer）的学生开设，其强化英语课程主要面对的是已获得无条件录取，但入学后，仍有提高语言能力需求的学生招生。*(2)(3)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>申请入口：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=srULj0RukXSVbKIeDDDDDD_yR95wRLOsvSiwRDtch6jaRUua0QjdWUAHjtbfrUNJoUSYoCmJrBwurEX' target='_blank'>online application form</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BkmLGCeMrLNMMMMMMuiXtru7-W_61NSW1PSlp0MOgI_nXjo8gZ5t404Ke9MIe8Mw2feb70L' target='_blank'>Programs Available</a> Columbia University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Gr-dDkhZk_OdHIw6hhhhhhvdFkbIi_qHc_PLRoPNdkG3IoLBRoGwzZ1BdkiNfkmNFbmBdtHNJ8yaF8y2JtFL' target='_blank'>Intensive Program</a> Columbia University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2uqLtcCKxY0CCCCCeewJz6PNndhn2j-p2G-oWU0FuCl6gJbxmKvsoSA21H9V1W9w2feb70LhijDrTjDcS_vajcqaksdJSR6xVz6ep4wMpq2UKXPBu4kn' target='_blank'>Advanced Academic Preparation</a> Columbia University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h1>研究生申请</h1><p><strong>院系设置</strong></p><p>哥伦比亚大学设有以下研究生院，分别是：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:20.24%">			<p>学院名称</p>			</td>			<td style="width:68.82%">			<p>学院英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:10.94%">			<p>成立时间</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:20.24%">			<p>内科与外科医师学院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:68.82%">			<p>College of Physicians and Surgeons</p>			</td>			<td style="width:10.94%">			<p>1767</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:20.24%">			<p>牙医学院</p>			<