工程（forensic (structural) engineering）、岩土工程（geotechnical engineering）及结构工程（structural engineering）。该系每年仅向秋季入学的硕士研究生提供一定的merit-based奖学金。*(5)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>哥伦比亚大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%9C%9F%E6%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B' target='_blank'>土木工程</a>与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>工程力学</a>系开设的研究领域包括：</p><ul>	<li>地震工程（Earthquake Engineering）</li>	<li>安全性与可靠性（Safety &amp; Reliability）</li>	<li>高级材料（Advanced Materials）</li>	<li>计算力学（Computational Mechanics）</li>	<li>交通工程（Transportation engineering）</li>	<li>环境与水利工程（Environmental Engineering and Water Resources）</li>	<li>飞行结构（Flight Structures）</li>	<li>流体力学（Fluid Mechanics）</li>	<li>岩土工程（Geotechnical Engineering）</li>	<li>基建交付与管理（Infrastructure Delivery and Management）</li>	<li>现代建筑材料（Modern Building Materials）</li>	<li>多重危害风险评估与缓解（Multi-Hazard Risk Assessment and Mitigation）</li>	<li>概率力学（Probabilistic Mechanics）</li>	<li>钢筋混凝土与预应力混凝土结构（Reinforced and Prestressed Concrete Structures）</li>	<li>固体力学（Solid Mechanics）</li>	<li>结构控制与健康监测（Structural Control and Health Monitoring）</li>	<li>结构动力学（Structural Dynamics）*(6)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJR6EwgqXDRxAjjjjjwzpDhm-nIvZj0eCcR1NTBh8nKhN30-HPOgRejNAVDu3VBH1EcYSXzJeFkCcR3epqAMCZxl8qALsS5CGy-lkVvxRJYDBfwgdzD2JDSbdwJZ1lQmrzeq_jK77VYDX' target='_blank'>Tuition Rates and Fees-Engineering, 2019&nbsp;- 20</a>20&nbsp;Columbia University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKNELAtGu9eDs-rnwuqxfXncOyVSKJe_jwdTt2lRU64xd-LMU9M-NMqNuMNiuYrwmoQ_yu_SSghxXAaGT--kx3M-GfwDrhFZCXYqKIsFbeeX--sntm-NDaBOn' target='_blank'>FAQ Standardized Test Scores</a> Columbia University</p><p>(3) <a href='https://gradengineering.columbia.edu/graduate-admissions/application-requirements' target='_blank'>Deadlines-Engineering</a> Columbia University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTdTLNk2B6