ref='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%99%BE%E5%88%86%E6%AF%94%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D' target='_blank'>百分比排名</a>多在64%以上，<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>数学</a>多在82%以上；不接受GMAT成绩*(2)</p><p>（6）该系研究生项目均接受秋季和春季学期入学申请，博士项目和MS项目秋季学期申请截止日期分别为12月15日和2月15日，春季学期申请截止日期均为10月1日*(3)</p><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>哥伦比亚大学地球与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B' target='_blank'>环境工程</a>系（Department of Earth and Environmental Engineering）研究生招收MS与PhD、D.Eng学生，要求申请者递交<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GRE' target='_blank'>GRE</a>成绩，但并无最低<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GRE' target='_blank'>GRE</a>、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GPA' target='_blank'>GPA</a>等分数要求。该系向学生提供<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/TA' target='_blank'>TA</a>、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/RA' target='_blank'>RA</a>、Fellowship等形式的<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%A5%96%E5%AD%A6%E9%87%91' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>，<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/TA' target='_blank'>TA</a><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%A5%96%E5%AD%A6%E9%87%91' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>一般只向第一年新生发放，<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/RA' target='_blank'>RA</a><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%A5%96%E5%AD%A6%E9%87%91' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>主要由导师发放。该系硕士与博士学生均有机会获得<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%A5%96%E5%AD%A6%E9%87%91' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>，但Fellowship一般只向博士学生发放。具体<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%A5%96%E5%AD%A6%E9%87%91' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>、申请方法等请见工程学院的申请说明。*(4)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>哥伦比亚大学地球与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B' target='_blank'>环境工程</a>系MS项目名为&ldquo;地球资源工程硕士（Master of Science in Earth resources engineering (M.S.-E.R.E.)）&rdquo;，共分三个专业方向，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>水资源与气候风险（Water Resources and Climate Risks）</li>	<li>可持续能源（Sustainable Energy）</li>	<li>可持续污染物管理（Integrated Waste Management）*(5)</li></ul><p>该系开设有以下三个研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>环境卫生工程（Environmental Health Engineering）</li>	<li>可持续能源与材料（Sustainable Energy And Materials）</li>	<li>水资源与气候风险（Water Resources and Climate Risks）*(6)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKNWLs_un1G5qqqqq_D78r4diE2LYW2hovzrt9dEqcd-ur-FCWXYflqAE1BQE6x9BkrFox0ANf62XnVlBkj2xR7yG3sArxe_bCZ9-my3TGSDWtf4XH5WH1BxSIDunHNZqgE5HL66nZJU' target='_blank'>Tuition Rates and Fees-Engineering, 2019&nbsp;- 20</a>20&nbsp;Columbia University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=CrXRF8zUkRbTQj5q9rwkPLY-hBUbZ4jCdcan--9km01hcOKkHUU6Wkj2CBmxSqkGFaG_QRGjxT4bRO3aHNANw_2oytxWDEYz2wOq6T8_yJyMAkuQ_2RwqAW5BUfy4' target='_blank'>FAQ Standardized Test Scores</a> Columbia University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23qqkW_gBhuYJqclrgU01C-4idkP8gNEfJAmUF3mwn8C6CdZQRe7K5RoALTbzIY_JieEsKnNCI8ZZngtw_kUTBhTlNPe7K8RcP' target='_blank'>Deadlines-Engineering</a> Columbia University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=8rL6TCNzkc7SCZBjkkkkkk84le8TuNgpMVZuwAIoXXONylOktrKNX4AtBDMDSxwOSVTO73ZvHd0sHTaQOt9FD4G3VcP-2g' target='_blank'>Funding Opportunities-EEE</a> Columbia University</p><p>(5) <a href='https://eee.columbia.edu/master-science-program-2' target='_blank'>Master of Science Degree-ERE</a> Columbia University</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nHC2kFr4DSSNyyyyyyegxYcP8B4mMVZuwAIoX6ha3ph16dP7v1BNb6F8gNEqLcRtHhSGPVgOA' target='_blank'>RESEARCH AREAS-EEE</a> Columbia University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>电气工程</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.04%">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D' target='_blank'>USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.44%">			<p>13</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.0%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.76%">			<p>$2,104/学分</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.24%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.54%">			<p>12月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.04%">			<p><a href