请说明</strong></p><p>哥伦比亚大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%94%B5%E6%B0%94%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B' target='_blank'>电气工程</a>系（Department of Electrical Engineering）研究生招收MS与PhD、D.Eng学生，要求申请者递交<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GRE' target='_blank'>GRE</a>成绩，但并无最低<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GRE' target='_blank'>GRE</a>、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GPA' target='_blank'>GPA</a>等分数要求。具体<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%A5%96%E5%AD%A6%E9%87%91' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>、申请方法等请见工程学院的申请说明。*(4)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>哥伦比亚大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%94%B5%E6%B0%94%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B' target='_blank'>电气工程</a>系开设的研究领域如下：</p><ul>	<li>信号与信息处理（Signal and Information Processing）</li>	<li>网络与通信（Networking and Communications）</li>	<li>集成电路与系统（Integrated Circuits and Systems）</li>	<li>系统生物学与神经工程（Systems Biology and Neuroengineering）</li>	<li>纳米结构及其整合设备（Nanoscale Structures and Integrated Devices）</li>	<li>智能电能（Smart Electric Energy）*(5)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=vrJH6YyhwkcdGH72XLfx0AhxD2tQfwHz0QN_QmN1zZ18xQJ6a1wZs8eIPbO9kEiubFYFGbu5jZptFN9XaPRmi1xUdBbeZhdqRM9N94nBvpu7hZf3hCilxgk06h2F_EtO_aFN3TTn2m7hlt8Yc4dB1wZ8d88Bh' target='_blank'>Tuition Rates and Fees-Engineering, 2019&nbsp;- 20</a>20&nbsp;Columbia University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=JrvWrUjkLbTirsihNNNNNNK4_e7oIzZMF546I-rVDNGkT7GkuBi7LYBspcSRJWfYJ6GiccQi56vFUsbke_8Me_-DwxBhwa0Dl5bF-PG0VAVoCADHTIGjW' target='_blank'>FAQ Standardized Test Scores</a> Columbia University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=urKrNASmkYo9iAIupoKQoQRx2xe2eDDmZ19WvoYaR8IgbdD9JY1Er8qrMWUQrJp0S3NRMIwk1DqN_sCMAg5-33g7IindQGY1EIYSKU' target='_blank'>Deadlines-Engineering</a> Columbia University</p><p>(4)<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=JrvWrUjtLqEHvP21bbbbbbLj20R8M7BnY4Y4fhzwXhaAH_CUWL6PJuqftYHctLHjJLMNtzEjRLMy' target='_blank'> ACADEMICS-EE</a> Columbia University</p><p>(5) <a rel