本科毕业，拥有物理、天文学或其相关领域学士学位，且具备强大的物理和数学背景。学生在攻读PhD学位期间，可授予文学硕士（MA）和哲学硕士（M.Phil）学位。该项目所有申请者可获得全额奖学金，涵盖全部学费、医疗保险和生活补助。*(4)(5)(6)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>天文学系有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>宇宙及其大尺度结构（Cosmology &amp; Large Scale Structure）</li>	<li>星系与星际物质（Galaxies &amp; the ISM）</li>	<li>高等天体物理（High Energy Astrophysics）</li>	<li>行星与起源（Planets &amp; Origins）</li>	<li>星球（Stars）</li>	<li>天文仪器（Instrumentation）</li>	<li>天文观测（Observational Astronomy）</li>	<li>模拟（Simulations）</li>	<li>理论（Theory）*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>天文学系导师列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=7r_i3IVFk2CbM-4Cm8o9uo_f_V2v12pUZelZgo9D3YGE_3kXpYg9IA1UiPRErQDexLxCdVICC-XB3GHCU4n0SU1_0HpIGjYk9BrEeM' target='_blank'>Astronomy Department Faculty</a></li>	<li>天文学系研究生项目手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=hrfXwivdLH56-BjJ666666YVfsFeAOqCLHRKRKPd4wNf6X7XApqiP9Lil7oEs36ZnKO0KlSr7lc2AMg6AvnJxvLDagLKvCJLH2oekV' target='_blank'>Astronomy Brochure</a> (pdf)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZiJLvi-JIsvcccccCdVfsFeAOqCgsFLZMrQPLDaWqDUC1XK2J-QO7j38IKY8LGekBd7iLNIwSRZyDG26lF9rfhTgVIbu_FxA1wKnMjkzZJs6kENai1oiPNRz4cyN-BUd9fctUCCQt6H' target='_blank'>2019-20&nbsp;Tuition</a> Columbia University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQuFrkQ2RhNW8GGGGGxLFg30RPnWZBHFRr-mSrG56woyUgoqSvoY1F9TF69B5NJTmNfAFo9TwQV8YJokrROuc-hpACt5r0BPTK9eTY7IMZGUxYOPLY9JLu9ITZGDLeF' target='_blank'>Application Procedures</a> Columbia University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2u0Lr9DfQt3SHDwGs-RFAnoqCWS3Iz0-nQ1tKtWs22MN-2O9SMMB9ayosYZi6hqIsAeenbkqN-7eGWD-re3_3appYwbpDEyoulrWX_1appY-CO5M75BstMT2tgB5Awca' target='_blank'>Information for International Students</a> Columbia University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhZWLs_unRgZTX9jDhrPe46nlmNhFLbLMLcj-9iCai5Jbq6_ttNvcmaQKaRQ-3WwcECdzVPshd7Gwembpa1ET2i-A0hQL_w3yypwF6AdoC