业方向，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>天体物理学（Astrophysics）</li>	<li>原子、分子与光子物理（Atomic, Molecular, &amp; Optical Physics）</li>	<li>凝聚态物质与激光物理（Condensed Matter &amp; Laser Physics）</li>	<li>核物理（Nuclear Physics）</li>	<li>粒子物理（Particle Physics）</li>	<li>理论物理（Theoretical Physics）*(8)</li></ul><p><strong>研究机构</strong></p><p>物理系除与天文学系、应用物理系、巴纳德物理系、电气工程系和数学系有密切的合作之外，还开设有以下研究中心、研究所和实验室，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>材料科学与研究工程中心（Materials Science and Research Engineering Center）</li>	<li>分子纳米结构电子传递中心（Center for Electron Transport in Molecular Nanostructures）</li>	<li>弦、宇宙与航天粒子物理研究所（ISCAP: Institute for Strings, Cosmology and Astroparticle Physics）</li>	<li>环境分子科学研究所（Environmental Molecular Science Institute）</li>	<li>哥伦比亚航天物理实验室（Columbia Astrophysics Laboratory）</li>	<li>微电子科学实验室/哥伦比亚辐射实验室（Microelectronics Sciences Laboratories/Columbia Radiation Laboratory）</li>	<li>尼维斯实验天体物理、核物理与粒子物理实验室（Nevis Laboratories）</li>	<li>纳米技术实验室（CEPSR Cleanroom）*(9)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzN0wI0Gi4nGiiiiih-dfGYO4BiepUPR1nucHw0eoO0bgc8QfHI4nVJrMEXFMHq_HzRxOI5vAnpXj6E7QbKItnuos1iaFRNQfU0hBh8ayfXlgX-RhE5aECDhU0oRxrNjRcMIrsllktfr' target='_blank'>2019-20&nbsp;Tuition</a> Columbia University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=urKrNAQ2L4yTxYwxooooo5WZplP6qL45TOlbpzjoRF-4bQ6rEqElcHpncfFzMZuvMy6YQI0V_12M6Q30oS9JnAOrSbcBw37heMZdz_Y8-YfauY1GJ6DREO19UWYvE93vo9ZaM_03uVr' target='_blank'>Application Procedures</a> Columbia University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Gr-dDkh-kSyncpb9LLLLLksi6lUiHwqXOobt39V2DNKXqyGlr9QNDw0gDZkwHprqPUkMyWtUVIsci_S4HpanXI7gWXL17S9mascRzsvh_Scl2S7BF1TQhWV6PrRhi' target='_blank'>Information for International Students</a> Columbia University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nqhwkcdGut9XXXXXX_JYiWKOwq8feN5ka4BjxWVXcGQUqMCZGU1ZA0AhZA1CLMHvVbhTc0BxbdOWCXwcCw2fgw7lgBCAcDUkw1XCkuoRkK' target='_blank'>Physics</a> Columbia University</p><p>