于MA和D.Ed之间的学位，该 项目要求申请者硕士毕业，拥有2年以上教学经验</li>	<li>D.Ed项目：要求申请者拥有3年教学经验，递交写作样本，并且每2年招生一次</li></ul><p><strong>具体项目设置如下：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>专业名称</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>专业英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>开设学位</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>课程与教学</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>Curriculum and Teaching</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>M.Ed、D.Ed</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>小学教育</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>Professional Certification in Elementary Education</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>MA</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>中学教育</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>Professional Certification in Secondary Education</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>MA</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>资优教育资格证书</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>Professional Certification Program leading to the Extension in Gifted Education</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>MA</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>小学强化教育资格证书（资优教育）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>Elementary Inclusive Education Initial Certification with Gifted Extension</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>MA</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>早期儿童教育</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>Early Childhood Education</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>MA、M.Ed、D.Ed</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>早期儿童政策</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>Early Childhood Policy</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>D.Ed</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:22.34%">			<p>早期儿童特殊教育</p>			</td>			<td style="width:56.98%">			<p>Early Childhood Special Education</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.7%">			<p>MA</p>			</td>		</tr>		<t