/p><p>（4）该专业要求GPA不低于3.0分，不接受GRE和GRE物理单项科目成绩*(5)</p><p>（5）职业疗法硕士要求TOEFL不低于100分，D.Ed要求TOEFL不低于100分，IELTS不低于7.0分*(6)</p><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>哥伦比亚大学职业疗法（Occupational Therapy）专业研究生阶段开设有以下学位项目，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>职业疗法硕士（MS in Occupational Therapy (Professional)）：为期1年，为希望成为职业治疗师的人士开设，经职业治疗教育认证委员会（ACOTE）认证，要求申请者本科毕业，不限专业背景，需修读过人体解剖学、生理学、心理学、社会学、人类学、英语写作、统计学、历史哲学等课程，还必须有职业治疗相关工作或志愿者经历*(7)(9)</li>	<li>职业疗法教育管理硕士（MS in Occupational Therapy Administration or Education (Postprofessional)）：为希望继续接受高等教育的职业治疗师开设*(9)</li>	<li>职业疗法硕士与公共卫生硕士双学位（MS in Occupational Therapy and Master of Public Health (Dual degree: both Professional and Post-professional)）*(9)</li>	<li>职业疗法博士（Doctor of Occupational Therapy，缩写：OTD）该项目为远程教育项目</li>	<li>运动科学教育博士（职业治疗）（Doctor of Education in Movement Science with a specialization in Occupational Therapy）：由内科与外科医师学院和师范学院共同开设，要求申请者职业治疗硕士毕业，且有一定的临床经验*(8)(9)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>运动科学教育学博士（职业治疗）项目宣传册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqV82wjNSr8X7tttttftbjNM5asolzFzFnCMUnC_eS6me2-KUkC9vjLobkxHlSNoUzrEv2CMlBdsndZYCr7shYjYHEtx81_UiTblum1vQLdt' target='_blank'>Ed.D. in Movement Science with a specialization in Occupational Therapy Brochure</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQ1Uws9rfULWQQQQQL1ke_8ACbPslXw69A0t3ik7mQkCelh0jqtDpMaHSTvQSrADbTvcCdIWmUEAxw4idg07v69q4tlP2c5KuJLS0woFgpJu6s1sLqajqbOe_KqWrC2g1y-VQvUU_leK' target='_blank'>Physicians and Surgeons</a> Occupational Therapy at Columbia University</p><p>(2) &nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFCELAtGuVrzyyyyyTD87BOm2ytI9ZXnXnR7eF6rEK51eY5l_5A7Xc28SjCb3W056FqoOcREZ9ZEzrdUCrmy4YfyauQ99fsy9fSAQuMNpX6BMNYCRRYqI0buPA' target='_blank'>Programs in Occupational Therapy MS Program 2015-16 Single Resident Student - Estimated Budget</a> Occupational Therapy at Columbia University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJElwvLQzwRg3333322MCaAX95