)(6)</p><p><strong>录取统计</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:28.64%">			<p>GPA分数范围</p>			</td>			<td style="width:27.44%">			<p>2.75-4.0</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.96%">			<p>GRE阅读均分</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.96%">			<p>152（53%）</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:28.64%">			<p>GRE数学均分</p>			</td>			<td style="width:27.44%">			<p>152（52%）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.96%">			<p>GRE写作均分</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.96%">			<p>4.0（49%）</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(7)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>物理疗法项目手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4e9kltmgDg0tttttNKxYcP8B4mFrKrKzdD7slV7OnReyOWawVOP9b47tkQmS04MwnACS0SCSbm8pV2CpkorcdUrXETtcZxQCJHtqJctWJcasUIF317QCE7CLsmRvBWE03WEr3e9Y2uyB2taA9' target='_blank'>Program in Physical Therapy 2015-2018 Bulletin</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2QqweEscz9Ag3YDmU1QV_TlR92dHBbPERmVfKQK6MUmldjbqXJV2jOddDGhCTnhssujw5NMdjECB5lu-dItDt4aAUzNGmrUQpA10KTqq4zHf-LrGjqTDFnTPglvN210DvUJ09NzM0-2CTPghQwi' target='_blank'>Physicians and Surgeons 2019-</a>20&nbsp;DPT at Columbia University</p><p>(2) &nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oaRwySz7kCTaaaqooojLySZFUJ4Vzk4ly7sg2ruF8uhFzrng3DZl8y10SbUtX9p0navN0sMVjTYb0JdRhpGI6pobcso2AJdRhpo5' target='_blank'>Instructions for Filing an Application</a> DPT at Columbia University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=xrVOpgS7wzOaRdoiqqqqqv_gx3N-678N_sD-HzKlHsQqDoALwovlRoEA_sWNYxEgYxnNwovi3VZRJcEz2qlzpsL3hZq1K6g1SRlzhulHWAey7fq3hZF_' target='_blank'>Information for International Students</a> DPT at Columbia University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2XBk6RIq_7_nnnq444eYJqE2-iwyhVwQJTgnA592l9F2h57nUeEYlTcnR1S7QLIKDKIXOLIZOLC6W71KrMaN0OVm' target='_blank'>Program Design</a> DPT at Columbia University</p><p>(5)